</span></p><p class="sc-EROOM ZMPII pf-212_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-d8f0969a-24b8-4393-9421-aa9d315f45e5"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Our innovative <a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/pages/complyplus-regulatory-compliance-management-software" target="_blank"><em><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);">ComplyPlus™</span></em></a> supports healthcare providers, care homes, and organisations across sectors in meeting regulatory standards, ensuring that chronic conditions like IBD are recognised and accommodated in policies and practices.
